<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 11:20:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国奢侈品市场“强劲反弹”，但疫情过后的不确定性依然存在</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3249766/chinas-luxury-goods-market-posts-robust-rebound-post-covid-uncertainties-remain?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>贝恩公司的数据显示，2023 年中国奢侈品市场同比增长 12%，但尽管仍被视为领先市场，挑战依然存在。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 11:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3249766/chinas-luxury-goods-market-posts-robust-rebound-post-covid-uncertainties-remain?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国金融科技巨头蚂蚁集团成立人工智能部门，由前谷歌研究员领导</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3249737/chinese-fintech-giant-ant-group-sets-ai-unit-led-former-google-researcher?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据知情人士透露，这个名为 NextEvo 的新部门将推动和协调蚂蚁金服的核心人工智能工作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 10:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3249737/chinese-fintech-giant-ant-group-sets-ai-unit-led-former-google-researcher?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院小组再次推动惩罚中国公司的贸易欺诈行为，警告这将对制造业造成“灾难性影响”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3249729/us-house-panel-renews-push-punish-trade-fraud-chinese-companies-warning-catastrophic-impact?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在俄亥俄州突袭中资汽车零部件供应商几天后，美国国会中国问题委员会对逃税和执法不严表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 10:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3249729/us-house-panel-renews-push-punish-trade-fraud-chinese-companies-warning-catastrophic-impact?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>江西火灾连续三起，习近平呼吁“深刻反思”事故频发</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3249751/chinese-leader-xi-jinping-calls-deep-reflection-frequent-accidents-deadly-jiangxi-fire-makes-it-3?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国国家主席习近平表示，当局应遏制“安全事故”频发的趋势，同时敦促地方政府帮助确保社会稳定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:13:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3249751/chinese-leader-xi-jinping-calls-deep-reflection-frequent-accidents-deadly-jiangxi-fire-makes-it-3?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国必须抓紧时间转向消费型经济</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3249150/why-china-must-waste-no-time-pivoting-consumption-based-economy?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>北京必须吸取日本和巴西的教训，这两个国家在过去几十年里实行了大量补贴的投资型经济，但由于消费空心化而崩溃。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 08:30:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3249150/why-china-must-waste-no-time-pivoting-consumption-based-economy?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国与新加坡达成最长30天免签协议</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3249746/china-singapore-agree-visa-free-deal-travel-stays-30-days?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>互免签证协议于今年2月9日农历除夕夜生效。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 08:06:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3249746/china-singapore-agree-visa-free-deal-travel-stays-30-days?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国解放军眼睁睁看着美国军舰穿越台湾海峡，此举是“挑衅”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3249719/pla-watches-us-warship-sails-through-taiwan-strait-provocative-move?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>第七舰队司令表示，驱逐舰的过境显示了美国对维护航行自由的承诺，而中国人民解放军发言人则指责美军“恶意”破坏该地区的和平与稳定。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 07:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3249719/pla-watches-us-warship-sails-through-taiwan-strait-provocative-move?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国春节旅游激增提振经济，但房地产市场和私营企业仍是首要任务</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3249720/chinas-lunar-new-year-travel-surge-boost-economy-property-market-and-private-firms-remain-top?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>周五开始的为期 40 天的年度“春运”旅游期间，中国境内的出行量将创下历史新高的 90 亿人次，但经济学家表示，确保 2024 年经济增长还有其他优先事项。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 06:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3249720/chinas-lunar-new-year-travel-surge-boost-economy-property-market-and-private-firms-remain-top?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>2024 AFF：代表们表示，中国促进债券和财富管理的政策将帮助香港公司和购房者</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3249707/2024-aff-chinas-policies-boost-bonds-and-wealth-management-will-help-hong-kongs-companies-and-home?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>新政策放宽了大湾区11个城市之间的跨境支付规则，方便港澳居民在华南地区购房。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 05:15:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3249707/2024-aff-chinas-policies-boost-bonds-and-wealth-management-will-help-hong-kongs-companies-and-home?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>欧盟表示中国的任何报复性贸易调查都必须“基于事实”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3249697/eu-says-any-retaliatory-trade-probe-china-must-be-based-facts?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>北京暗示将反击欧洲的贸易措施，其中包括对中国电动汽车行业的行业补贴进行审查。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 04:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3249697/eu-says-any-retaliatory-trade-probe-china-must-be-based-facts?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国将高科技创新视为其全球竞争力和制造业主导地位的福音</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3249642/china-sees-hi-tech-innovation-boon-its-global-competitiveness-and-manufacturing-dominance?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>新公布的计划将创建五个试点设施，将中国的研发和创新理念（来自实验室和研究论文）转化为商业上可行的应用。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 02:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3249642/china-sees-hi-tech-innovation-boon-its-global-competitiveness-and-manufacturing-dominance?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>乔·拜登否决了阻止电动汽车充电站“购买美国货”豁免的努力</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3249675/joe-biden-vetoes-law-blocking-ev-charging-stations-buy-america-waiver?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登表示，这项豁免将利用联邦拨款加快充电站的生产，外国内容的补贴将于 7 月 1 日之前逐步取消。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 22:32:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3249675/joe-biden-vetoes-law-blocking-ev-charging-stations-buy-america-waiver?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国人民银行“指导”申请，蚂蚁集团支持的信用评分公司钱塘江在等待两年后更接近获得中国牌照</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3249658/ant-group-backed-credit-scorer-qiantang-closer-licence-china-after-two-year-wait-pboc-guide?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>官员表示，经过两年多的等待，这家信用评分公司似乎即将获得正式批准开始运营，并由中国人民银行指导其申请。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 22:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3249658/ant-group-backed-credit-scorer-qiantang-closer-licence-china-after-two-year-wait-pboc-guide?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国GDP：债务危机影响各省制定保守的2024年经济增长目标</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3249636/china-gdp-provinces-set-conservative-2024-economic-growth-targets-debt-hangover-bites?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>北京已要求债务缠身的地方政府重组债务并控制支出，北方直辖市天津设定了2024年国内生产总值(GDP)增长4.5%的目标。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 22:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3249636/china-gdp-provinces-set-conservative-2024-economic-growth-targets-debt-hangover-bites?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>北京如何让统一对台湾人更具吸引力</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3249396/how-beijing-can-make-reunification-more-appealing-taiwanese?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着“一个国家、两种制度”的方案失宠，北京可能需要跳出框框思考，制定出更加自由和包容的宪法方案。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 21:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/article/3249396/how-beijing-can-make-reunification-more-appealing-taiwanese?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>